org.intermine.objectstore.query

Class QueryField

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.objectstore.query.QueryField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryEvaluable, QueryNode, QueryOrderable, QuerySelectable

    public class QueryField
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryEvaluable
    Represents a QueryClass field that is neither a collection or reference to another business object.
